============
sciencedates
============
Date conversions used in the sciences.

.. contents::

Install
=======
::

    python -m pip install -e .


Examples
========

.. code:: python

    from pytz import UTC
    from datetime import datetime
    import sciencedates as sd

    T = datetime(2013,7,2,12,0,0,tzinfo=UTC)
    yd,utsec=sd.datetime2yd(T)


